reviewText: One of her best performances ever, in the early 1990's, when she was at the very peak of her singing skills.  Every song was sung with perfection, and with passion.  The ending to her "Working Man" was the most beautiful sounding ever!  Some of the songs on this VHS were "Thinking of You," "I'll Accept the Rose," "Shining Strong," "Hone I'll Be," "Old Man," "Flying on Your Own," and the amazing performance of "Working Man" at the very end.  There are several other songs that I'm thinking of right off hand, and all were sung with perfection!
